        <detaileddescription>
<para>every control point of the spline is moved to the closest point on the given mesh; every not-control point of the spline is moved to the closest point in the region between two control points Generated from function <computeroutput>MR::projectSpline</computeroutput>. Parameter <computeroutput>mesh</computeroutput> can not be null. It is a single object. Parameter <computeroutput>spline</computeroutput> can not be null. It is a single object. Never returns null. Returns an instance allocated on the heap! Must call <computeroutput><ref refid="std__vector__MR__Vector3f_8h_1abab6d7c953a1806ebeb1b7e736c18d49" kindref="member">MR_std_vector_MR_Vector3f_Destroy()</ref></computeroutput> to free it when you&apos;re done using it. </para>
